dct_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines for Ellis' Island, New Jersey, New York Harbor as recommended by the New York Harbor Line Board
dct_description_sm: Map shows the bulkhead and pierhead lines, a bulkhead line approved by the Secretary of War February 1st 1890, soundings and Ellis Island with its pier and bulkhead lines.
